                            36. Ayo translate kalimat romantis dibawah ini ke dalam bahasa inggris:
Aku tahu keadaan dan posisi kita meskipun tidak seluruhnya. Dari awal masing-masing dari kita pasti sudah memikirkan ini. Tapi, kita tidak bisa menolak kepada siapa kita jatuh cinta. Yang hanya bisa kita lakukan hanya menahannya atau melanjutkannya. Jadi, selama kita masih bisa berkomunikasi, dekat dan selama kamu mau, aku berusaha baik kepadamu. Nikmati saja. Segala kemungkinan tidak pernah 0% meskipun hanya 0,01%. Tetaplah berdoa.</h2><br />
                        I know the situation and our position though not entirely. From the beginning of each of us would have thought of this. But, we can not refuse to whom we fall in love. That only we can do is hold it or continue it. So, while we still can communicate, close and as long as you want, I'm trying to better you. Just enjoy it. Everything possible is never 0% although only 0.01%. Keep praying.I know the situation and our position though not entirely. From the beginning of each of us would have thought of this. But, we can not refuse to whom we fall in love. That only we can do is hold it or continue it. So, while we still can communicate, close and as long as you want, I'm trying to better you. Just enjoy it. Everything possible is never 0% although only 0.01%. Keep praying.<br /><br />Semoga Membantu, Tolong jadikan yang terbaik ^_^ <br /><br />Thanks.<br />
